  <div id="zhiyan-tab-bar"><button class="zhiyan-tab active" id="tab-cs" onclick="switchTab('cs')">💬 客服</button><button class="zhiyan-tab" id="tab-legal" onclick="switchTab('legal')">⚖️ 法律諮詢</button></div>
  <div id="zhiyan-chat-messages" class="zhiyan-tab-panel"><div class="zhiyan-msg ai">嗨！我是智小研 👋 有什麼想了解的嗎？</div></div>
  <div id="zhiyan-legal-messages" class="zhiyan-tab-panel" style="display:none"><div class="zhiyan-msg ai">您好！我是智小研法律助手 ⚖️ 請問有什麼法律問題需要協助？</div></div>
  <div id="zhiyan-rag-bar" style="display:none"></div>
